  <num>1-328.06</num>
  <heading proof="needed">Cultural and community affairs grants.</heading>
  <para>
    <num>(a)</num>
    <text>The Mayor may issue grants, in accordance with the requirements set forth in <cite path="1|3|XII-A|B">part B of this subchapter</cite>, to individuals and organizations that provide services to District residents to support cultural affairs, community relations, and community partnerships.</text>
  </para>
  <para>
    <num>(b)</num>
    <text>The Mayor shall provide centralized review and approval of grants issued pursuant to:</text>
    <para>
      <num>(1)</num>
      <text><cite path="§2-1313|(10)">§ 2-1313(10)</cite>;</text>
    </para>
    <para>
      <num>(2)</num>
      <text><cite path="§2-1392|(c)|(10)">§ 2-1392(c)(10)</cite>;</text>
    </para>
    <para>
      <num>(3)</num>
      <text><cite path="§2-1398.02|(b)|(3)">§ 2-1398.02(b)(3)</cite>;</text>
    </para>
    <para>
      <num>(4)</num>
      <text><cite path="§2-1373|(c)|(9)">§ 2-1373(c)(9)</cite>;</text>
    </para>
    <para>
      <num>(5)</num>
      <text>§§<cite path="§2-1383|(b)|(11)">2-1383(b)(11)</cite>, <cite path="§2-1383|(b)|(11A)">(11A)</cite>, and <cite path="§2-1383|(b)|(12)">(12)</cite> and <cite path="§2-1384">2-1384</cite>;</text>
    </para>
    <para>
      <num>(6)</num>
      <text><cite path="§3-1452|(b)|(3)">§ 3-1452(b)(3)</cite>;</text>
    </para>
    <para>
      <num>(7)</num>
      <text><cite path="§24-1302|(b)|(2)|(L)">§ 24-1302(b)(2)(L)</cite>; and</text>
    </para>
    <para>
      <num>(8)</num>
      <text><cite path="§49-1003|(6A)">§ 49-1003(6A)</cite>.</text>
    </para>
  </para>
